LIVE MUSIC BEGINS AT 8:00 PM ON NEW YEAR'S EVE!

If you can't join us for our 4-course dining, wine & bourbon experience, you are welcome to party with us - cocktails, live rocking music, Packers vs Vikings game, and our late-night bites menu! This event is open to members and the public, no RSVP is required for this portion of the evening.

7:00-Midnight: Cocktail Cash Bar, Live Music, and Late-Night Bites Menu serving 8:30-10:30pm
